summary: 01/03/1993: Two male members of HAMAS stabbed and killed Mr. Haim Nahmani, an Israeli intelligence agent, in West Jerusalem, Israel.
corp1: Agent for the Israeli Shin Beth Intelligence Service
weapdetail: Haim Nahmani was stabbed and beaten with a hammer.
addnotes: Haim Nahmani had arranged to meet a HAMAS informant, but was attacked and killed prior to the meeting.
scite1: “HAMAS militant kills Israeli intelligence agent: minister,” Agence France Presse, January 3, 1993.
scite2: “Agent Killed in Palestinian Attack,” The Associated Press, January 3, 1993.
scite3: Jonathan Ferziger, “Police Search for Killer of Shin-Bet Agent,” United Press International, January 4, 1993.
